query:
INSERT INTO releases (
                    release_intent_id,
                    project_id,
                    destination_id,
                    status
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4
                )
                ON CONFLICT (project_id, destination_id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    release_intent_id = EXCLUDED.release_intent_id,
                    status = EXCLUDED.status,
                    updated = now()
